2.0.0.name: drupal/realistic_dummy_content_api

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

2.0.0.description: Allows enabled modules to generate kick-ass demo content (see the Realistic Dummy Content module for an example of how to do this). Do not enable on production sites.
